{"tid":1768861,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"葉劍英孫女葉晴晴係香港歌唱組合Robynn & Kendy成員","createTime":"2019-12-04T11:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T12:11:08.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3c1f0cad85ddc39e0dda85600f6d9a57db410c60","tid":1768861,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180118/photo/bkn-20180118112452759-0118_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180118180740\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180118%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180118112452759-0118_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180118180740&h=9a6bd0f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>揭秘葉氏三姐妹奢華生活</strong><br />\n香港女孩Robynn和Kendy以一曲齊秦的《思念是一種病》改編版把全場觀眾帶入高潮。其清新的樂風和默契的和聲引起了齊秦、那英、楊坤三位導師的爭搶。節目播出後,Robynn的身世隨之被網友曝光,原來Robynn的真名是葉晴晴,是開國元勛葉劍英的孫女,葉選廉的女兒,現為環球唱片旗下藝人。很多網友都對葉家三姐妹的身份有所好奇,今日就為大家揭秘下這個神奇的家庭。<br />\n<br />\n葉晴晴畢業於美國西北大學,主修心理學,曾在自閉症兒童訓練中心任職語言治療師,葉晴晴從小就具備音樂天賦,大學時曾參與無伴奏合唱團,獲得過音樂比賽冠軍,還曾邀請到新加坡及台灣等地演出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=jc3ia5/2311/5005049922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Djc3ia5%2F2311%2F5005049922.jpg&h=2a0565d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=1ag4dht/2309/5582512851.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D1ag4dht%2F2309%2F5582512851.jpg&h=587bf013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n值得一提的是,當時Robynn在嘉興錄製當期盲選時,其父葉選廉也在現場為女兒加油。圖為:葉晴晴(左)和父親葉選廉(中)、姐姐葉明子(右)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=15jvctn/2310/4916936514.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D15jvctn%2F2310%2F4916936514.jpg&h=fbab5d61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=1cpbua5/2306/6475257115.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D1cpbua5%2F2306%2F6475257115.jpg&h=07238c44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=2p49rae/2309/5582278004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2p49rae%2F2309%2F5582278004.jpg&h=43fd752f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=3801fho/2304/7552534128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D3801fho%2F2304%2F7552534128.jpg&h=9c38fae1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac9cf43e025948f90ca77af59aada90944d4c2d3","tid":1768861,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:23:51.000Z","msg":"明澤呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7bb47e4b9bb2d7c7d54c549749dbea31acef52e","tid":1768861,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:27:22.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下，特首選委過半有望。<br />\n<br />\n特首選委戰線 &mdash; 七個同行手足，成立工會，重光勞工界！只剩唔夠四個月時間！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"84e9243638ad784a32e5411af7dd2686403ffd66","tid":1768861,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T12:11:08.000Z","msg":"太高調<br />\n<br />\n出事嫁嘛"}]}